Try to get 801.11ac USB dongle to work:
* Download .deb for kernel-headers from https://www.niksula.hut.fi/~mhiienka/Rpi/linux-headers-rpi/
* apt install gcc-4.7
* apt install git
* git clone http://github.com/diederikdehaas/rtl8812AU
* cd rtl8812AU/
* vi Makefile 
ARCH := arm
* make
* sudo make
* sudo make install
Give up in disgust.

Try to get RTL 8188CUS to work as hostapd:
$ wget https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/1663660/scripts/install-rtl8188cus.sh
Update /etc/hostapd/hostapd.conf
Remove br0 from /etc/network/interfaces
Reboot


